# ABS Resolve — Variáveis de Ambiente

## Backend (`backend/.env`)

```env
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://abs:abs123@localhost:5432/abs_resolve"
JWT_SECRET="your-jwt-secret"
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET="your-refresh-secret"
JWT_EXPIRES_IN="15m"
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN="7d"
PORT=3001
FRONTEND_URL="http://localhost:5173"

# Asaas (sandbox — deixe vazio para modo mock)
ASAAS_API_KEY=""
ASAAS_API_URL="https://sandbox.asaas.com/api/v3"

# SMTP (deixe vazio para registrar notificações sem enviar)
SMTP_HOST=""
SMTP_PORT="587"
SMTP_USER=""
SMTP_PASS=""
SMTP_FROM="noreply@absresolve.com.br"

# WhatsApp (Evolution API)
WHATSAPP_TOKEN=""
WHATSAPP_API_URL=""
```

## Frontend (`frontend/.env`)

```env
VITE_API_URL=/api
```

## Como rodar

```bash
# 1. Subir PostgreSQL
docker compose up -d

# 2. Migrar e popular banco
cd backend
npm run db:migrate
npm run db:seed

# 3. Backend (terminal 1)
npm run dev

# 4. Frontend (terminal 2)
cd ../frontend
npm run dev
```

